- To install this module you need to install:
     + eBox components
        libebox
	ebox
	network
	objects
     + Debian packages
        iptables
     + a Netfilter enabled linux kernel 

- Once all dependencies are satisfied, type:
	
	./configure
	make install

  configure will autodetect eBox base path to install

- Update your sudoers file with the ebox-sudoers command.
